snippet.title: And Soon the Darkness - Trailer
snippet.description: Welcome to the AC Show Movie Trailers! Today's movie is: And Soon the Darkness. See you later with the news of today! This horror thriller is the first movie directed by Marcos Efron.  It's a remake of And Soon the Darkness from the 70s by Robert Fuest. Amber Heard and Odette Yustman are Ellie and Stephanie, two young Americans on a bike trip to Argentina. Everything seems perfect until Ellie disappears mysteriously. Stephanie turns first to the local police and then to Michael, an American played by Karl Urban. The film comes out in the theaters Dec. 17.
